## ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

**Frontend:**
- Next.js
- React.js
- Tailwind CSS
- Redux Toolkit
- Framer Motion

**Backend:**
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Redis
- WebSockets (Socket.io)

**Third-Party APIs:**
- OpenAI (Chatbot, PDF QA)
- ZegoCloud (Audio/Video Calling)
- Twilio (Messaging Support)
- Stripe / PayPal (Payments)
- Google APIs (Auth, Maps, etc.)

**Auth & Security:**
- JWT
- NextAuth.js
- Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

